JOHANNESBURG - eNCA's Moneyline runs a weekly feature in which well-known South Africans chat about their relationship with money.This week, it's comedian Mark Banks' turn.Banks said he loves to travel and splurges on overseas holidays."The moment I've got enough money to travel -- if I've got enough money and the time -- then I'm gone," he said.He also spoke about his first job and salary and gave a few money tips.eNCA